node.text: Well my son is a man today😔! I'm so blessed to be your father! The focus, determination, competetive fire, compassion, love and leadership you possess inspires me daily! You gave me a reason to keep pushing when i wanted to quit, and a reason to fight for. You accepted me for who i am, and the friendship and bond we have is unbreakable. Thank you for being such an amazing kid, and making parenting easy! I got your back for life, and support all you do. You are a conqueror, and God smiles when angles speak of you. I love you @tjwooodley HAPPY BIRTHDAY! Follow the future if you follow me and help me wish him a HBD!
